        "content": "## \u2601\ufe0f  Pod Resource Scanner\nOpen-source Kubernetes capacity & cost scanner by **[CloudDrove](https://clouddrove.com)** \u00b7 [GitHub \u2197](https://github.com/clouddrove/pod-resource-scanner)\n\nScan CPU, memory, OOM kills, ResourceQuotas, HPAs, and cost estimates across all namespaces. Export to CSV, Google Sheets, and Prometheus.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "9.0.0",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 86400
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 604800
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 5,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
